datest                  Compute estimated series from neighbour stations
depudm                  Study the homogeneity of monthly data
depstat                 Compute averages for some period
destipif                Unstandardize the series
diagwl                  Walter & Lieth climatic diagram
grabeps                 Save the last graph (in EPS)
grafanom                Plot anomalies, and data plus estimated data
leerdm                  Read the monthly data, with optional
			transformation a+b*x
matpesos                Compute the inter-station wheight matrix
movttest                t-test for a running window
rosavent                Plot a wind-rose
tipif                   Standardize the series
